&lt;p&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;SIA &amp;quot;NT Group&amp;quot; is founded in the 2008th the union of metalworking areas with the high class and experienced professionals, and become a dynamic and productive Latvian metal products and constructions field company.&lt;br /&gt;
	The company begins its way back to the 1999th year, when it specialized in the metal treatment and operated under a different name. Currently, the company has developed its operations to several areas of the metal industry.&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Examples of work:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Steel building construction.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Building modules, made of light metal structures.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Industrial buildings.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Warehouse buildings.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Pavilions, stairways, doors, hatches, fencing, decorative elements, as well as any other type of products from the black and stainless steel.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		Repair of fabricated metal products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
